<p>Cryptographer Ben Laurie also makes the point about efficiency on a global protocol level, but sometimes it&#8217;s not always about efficiency. See my comment to Ben&#8217;s thesis here: <a href="http://www.links.org/?p=1183#comment-488956" rel="nofollow">http://www.links.org/?p=1183#comment-488956</a></p>
