        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-15729" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-15729" class="dsq-comment-message"><p> &gt; Except that this service isn&#8217;t a normal, honest free market offer<br />
Yes, it&#8217;s a very normal free market offer.</p>
<p>Also, if it&#8217;s clearly indicated that a certain game is using your GPU for other purposes it&#8217;s also very honest.</p>
<p>A complete offer to play the game could let the player decide if using the GPU or pay for it.</p>
</div>
